{"id":"eliphalet","term":"Eliphalet","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>God his deliverance, one of David’s sons (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 5:16\">2 Sam. 5:16</a>); called also Eliphelet (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 3:8\">1 Chr. 3:8</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 5:16","1 Chronicles 3:8"]}